'''Nomsa Kupi Manaka''' (wavutse 1962) ni umubyinnyi  n'umukinnyi wa filime , umukinnyi wa koreografi wo muri [[Afurika yepfo]]

== Ubuzima bwa Biografiya ==
Manaka yavutse 1962 i Orlando, mu mujyi wa Soweto muri Johannesburg,  [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]]. Amaze gutozwa ballet ya kera, yigisha kubyina muri Funda Centre, yashinzwe numugabo we, Matsemela Manaka.  Mu 1989, yakinnye mu ikinamico, ''Gorée'', yashyize aha hantu hateranira imbata zerekeza muri Amerika, kandi zivuga ku rugendo rwo mu mwuka rw'umukobwa ukiri muto. Uyu mugore yiga kubyina nyafurika, bimuganisha ku kwishakira ibisubizo. Azenguruka umugabane arangirira i Gorée, muri Senegali. Agezeyo, ahura n’umugore ukuze, wakinwe na Sibongile Khumalo, amufasha kumenya umurage we nyafurika. <ref name="dico2013" /> <ref>https://www.nytimes.com/1989/09/24/theater/review-theater-a-homily-in-african-song-and-dance.html</ref>

Mu 1991, Manaka yashinze ikinyamakuru cy'imbyino, ''Umukororombya w'Amizero'',  maze akora choreografiya, harimo n'iya opera ''Umukobwa wa Nebo'', mu 1993. <ref>https://www.nytimes.com/1994/03/05/arts/review-theater-mystic-vs-rational-in-south-africa.html</ref> Mu bihangano bye bya koreografiya, ahuza imigenzo nyafurika ndetse nuburyo bwo kubyina byubu. <ref name="dico2013" /> Umugabo we, Matsemela Manaka, yapfuye mu 1998 azize impanuka y'imodoka. <ref>https://www.brandsouthafrica.com/people-culture/arts-culture/manaka-markettheatre</ref>

Mu mwaka wa 2010, Manaka yagaragaye muri filime ngufi ya Tiisetso Dladla yayobowe na ''Exiled'', ivuga ku mugore wumvikanye mu buhungiro bwe muri politiki muri Amerika mu 1990. <ref>https://www.goldposter.com/movie/10712763/</ref> Mu myaka ya za 2010, yabanaga n'umucuranzi Hugh Masekela, wari urwaye kanseri ya prostate . We ubwe yari yarasuzumwe kanseri yintanga mu 2016. Yavuze ku kuntu babona iyi ndwara ati: "Byari ngombwa ko twembi twohereza ubutumwa ko tugomba kwishimira ubuzima bwacu n'abo turi bo. Ntidukwiye kureka kanseri ikatumanura. " Hugh Masekela yapfuye muri Mutarama 2018. Manaka yakize indwara nyuma y'amezi ya chimiotherapie. <ref>https://www.timeslive.co.za/tshisa-live/tshisa-live/2018-01-29-bra-hughs-last-love-nomsa-manaka-he-was-the-most-amazing-person/</ref> Mu gihe cyo gukira kwe, Manaka yazanye igitekerezo cyo kubyina kubyina ''Dance Out of Kanseri'', yaberaga kuri Theatre Joburg yo gukusanya amafaranga ku barwayi ba kanseri. <ref>https://www.sowetanlive.co.za/entertainment/2017-06-22-nomsa-manaka-dances-out-of-cancer/</ref>

